						<summary>

						<p>This inscription registers gift of 160 pon to the temple of Kumbīśvaramuḍaiya mahādēva at Vikramaśiṅga chaturvēdimaṅgalam in Dāmaṟnāḍu a sub-division of Dāmaṟkōṭṭam in Jayaṅgoṇḍachōḻamaṇḍalam. Mentions a person Karambiseṭṭu Chōḻapirān, one of the <hi rend="italic">āḷuṅgaṇattārs</hi>, as signatory.</p>						

						</summary>
